&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="inner_cell"&gt;
&lt;div class="text_cell_render border-box-sizing rendered_html"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I started to list everything you would need but I have not managed to find a starting point (should I start with how to install pip or should I tell you where to buy your computer?). Other people have made excellent tutorials (I will make the links in the last chapter) so I'll assume that you already have some knowledge:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;need a &lt;a href="http://github.com"&gt;github account&lt;/a&gt; of course&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;install &lt;a href="http://getnikola.com"&gt;nikola&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;install &lt;a href="http://ipython.org/install.html"&gt;ipython notebook&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
